name: deterioration_sequence_arbitrary_no_23
description:
"I mint them for .08 tez and I sell them for .07 tez. People ask me why. I’ll tell you why, man– they are holy NFTs [...] and that is why I cannot allow myself any profit on them."

 “I’ll give you .05 tez.”

 “Terrific, man, that’s even better for my soul, I’ll be losing tokens."
